{"tid":2003441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上年拋過壁屋，你問我盡答","createTime":"2020-05-05T21:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T08:30:56.000Z","uid":96501,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd1cb3eee8e5398b40a564b4e933408698ff95d","tid":2003441,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:26:16.000Z","msg":"借朋友acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年4月同6月拋過壁屋court仔同二倉，兩次都係14日<br />\n同一條褲所以唔使問我係咪因為運動而入去<br />\n<br />\n今日見到有手足係入面比柳記打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有關入面嘅嘢如果大家有咩想知可以喺度問"},{"pid":"c721dd20acb27d846841f2fa0b5bebee09ccb636","tid":2003441,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdfdb01ac9ae4372bca5976a486312fada894f9","tid":2003441,"uid":21527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:32:27.000Z","msg":"未夠18？有無比人打腳板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af4a55b3f9955775b94badd6e09540f320562cb","tid":2003441,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bbdfdb01ac9ae4372bca5976a486312fada894f9","tid":2003441,"uid":21527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:32:27.000Z","msg":"未夠18？有無比人打腳板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:36:18.000Z","msg":"過咗18，6月果轉差一日生日夠21就跌咗入DCR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（夠21歲係YADCR，兩種待遇嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n老實講我兩次都冇比柳記打過，落手多數係B仔（即係幫阿Sir做嘢嘅犯）"},{"pid":"e02c29b663af350cf301e62c144cf86a00139f17","tid":2003441,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:39:11.000Z","msg":"等陣食咩早餐"},{"pid":"4b9aa1fe757fb28079977dfb77416427e85e0586","tid":2003441,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e02c29b663af350cf301e62c144cf86a00139f17","tid":2003441,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:39:11.000Z","msg":"等陣食咩早餐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:41:44.000Z","msg":"雞翼，應該配士多啤梨汁/黑汁"},{"pid":"8294632b167c075ae5563ae86a9be0f032fbd6cb","tid":2003441,"uid":21527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:45:14.000Z","msg":"21歲聽講好hea唔會打，同阿sir吹下水又一日，但21以個d成日辱鳩d𡃁仔"},{"pid":"8bf67dae2546fa5eaee6ecd86a996664e45c7bf3","tid":2003441,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8294632b167c075ae5563ae86a9be0f032fbd6cb","tid":2003441,"uid":21527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:45:14.000Z","msg":"21歲聽講好hea唔會打，同阿sir吹下水又一日，但21以個d成日辱鳩d𡃁仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:50:37.000Z","msg":"呢個真，YA唔會打，又唔使步操，係倉睇吓書寫下信又一日<br />\n不過正常來講YA係要去做廚雜（即刻去廚房幫手清垃圾同送飯/包奶，啲垃圾勁污糟又重又臭，好撚辛苦），但我嗰期YA唔夠人就變咗我地DCR做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd78df47f5ecac0d07aef497897574d1b5989b7","tid":2003441,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:52:46.000Z","msg":"死監躉，垃圾"},{"pid":"8717a407e4ac1e5e746c19a93285e690e9efed91","tid":2003441,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebd78df47f5ecac0d07aef497897574d1b5989b7","tid":2003441,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:52:46.000Z","msg":"死監躉，垃圾"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:57:45.000Z","msg":"知唔撚知咩叫拋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/